        "timestamp": 1749507514
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>For example here I override the default value with my own implementation</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">example</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">State</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kn\">where</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">labels</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"dummy_labels\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">val_labels</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"s2\">\"label_zero\"</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"label_one\"</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">typeMap</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"type_zero\"</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"o\">),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"type_one\"</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Int</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">×</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Bool</span><span class=\"o\">),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"type_two\"</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Unit</span><span class=\"o\">)]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">val</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"s2\">\"type_zero\"</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">17</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"s2\">\"type_two\"</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">8</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"s2\">\"type_one\"</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">777</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"s2\">\"type_one\"</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">42</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">lemma_1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">decide</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">lemma_2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">decide</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
